01:37.176 --> 01:40.881
It made me feel weak and like I was dragging other people down with my problems.

01:41.802 --> 01:52.114
But the truth is that only after I took off the filter of pretending things were better than they were, I began to experience some hint of relief, healing, and hope.

01:53.122 --> 01:55.748
