34:27.428 --> 34:30.994
The day that the prophet speaks of, the day where he says,

34:31.170 --> 34:45.325
The realities and broken patterns of our families will one day not have to have a hold on us anymore just because a parent or a grandparent or a great-grandparent made decisions doesn't mean it will have to impact future generations.

34:45.605 --> 34:58.258
That hopeful day that the prophet declared is the day of Jesus that we read about later in 1 Corinthians, where we read that Jesus, by his death and resurrection, breaks the curse of death.

34:58.434 --> 35:19.034
And if the curse of death cannot stand in the power of Jesus' death and resurrection, then there is no curse, no pattern, no series of brokenness, no decisions of the past that cannot be torn down, that cannot be overcome by the same death and resurrection, the life and hope of Jesus.

35:19.835 --> 35:27.602
But friends, it will take being honest, having courage to be honest about where we are,

35:28.034 --> 35:28.915
and how we got here.

35:29.756 --> 35:34.042
You see, the enemy tries to teach us that we need to be ashamed and afraid to go there.

35:35.383 --> 35:44.475
But the light and life of Jesus, the way that Jesus offers life and resurrection for us, while that is an invitation to courage.

35:45.236 --> 35:49.461
So I encourage you to step into that space.

35:51.164 --> 35:56.210
There is nothing so broken, no decision that's happened in your family,

35:56.450 --> 36:05.839
None, no action that you have taken that cannot be overcome by the power of Jesus, his death, and his resurrection.

36:07.320 --> 36:13.807
And so what we do with that then is press into that space of relationship with him.

36:14.588 --> 36:20.493
So if you've not yet received the gift of Jesus and the life that he offers, then today is your day.

36:20.814 --> 36:25.458
Today is the day of rescue in a new way that he has for you.

36:26.178 --> 36:36.754
So I invite you, if you've not yet done that, then ask right now for Jesus to be the one who brings life and life and purpose and adventure into your life.

36:37.295 --> 36:39.598
To be the one who makes your family new.

36:40.560 --> 36:43.184
Confess with your mouth that you need him.

36:43.785 --> 36:49.874
Ask him to be the one who rescues and leads you and your family and watch what God does.

36:50.850 --> 36:55.575
Now, once we've done that, there's another passage of Scripture I want to point to really quickly.

36:55.595 --> 36:59.980
