45:07.957 --> 45:13.906
I'm going to pray for us that we would be found faithful stepping into this new path.

45:14.018 --> 45:15.840
this new way.

45:16.401 --> 45:27.453
And as I do, I leave you with this invitation from the prophet Jeremiah, where he says, set up road signs, set up guideposts, take note of the highway, the road that you take.

45:27.513 --> 45:32.960
In other words, choose a new path, the path of love today.

45:34.121 --> 45:36.604
Let's pray.

45:36.624 --> 45:38.346
God, you are the God of life.

45:39.307 --> 45:41.970
Jesus, you are the one who overcame death.

45:42.786 --> 45:47.353
who rose again and because of that, there is no curse that binds us.

45:48.014 --> 45:49.716
There is no pattern that we're stuck in.

45:50.257 --> 45:52.260
There is nothing that you can't free us from.

45:53.582 --> 46:08.865
And so on behalf of my brothers and sisters, whatever their circumstance or situation, I pray that you would reveal yourself as the curse-breaking God, as the one who turns what was meant for a curse into a blessing, as the one who leads us in a new path down the way of love.

46:10.067 --> 46:12.210
Show us what that looks like for each of us today.

46:12.994 --> 46:13.897
and give us courage.

46:14.780 --> 46:16.746
Oh God of the holy courage.

46:17.648 --> 46:22.283
To be honest about where we are and how we got here, and to take a step down the new path.

46:23.025 --> 46:24.329
We ask this in Jesus' name.

46:25.593 --> 46:25.874
Amen.

